## 🔌 Full API Reference

### Products — `/api/v1/products`
| Method | URL | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/products` | List all products (paginated) |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/products/:id` | Get by ObjectId **or** slug |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/products` | Create a new product |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/products/:id` | Update product |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/products/:id` | Soft-delete (sets status → inactive) |

**Query params (GET list):** `?filter=organic&search=urea&featured=true&page=1&limit=20`

---

### Enquiries — `/api/v1/enquiries`
| Method | URL | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/enquiries` | Submit farmer enquiry *(public)* |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/enquiries` | List all enquiries *(admin)* |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/enquiries/:id/status` | Update status + adminNote *(admin)* |

**POST body:** `name, phone, village, product, message` (required) + `crop` (optional)  
**PATCH body:** `{ "status": "seen" | "replied" | "closed", "adminNote": "..." }`  
**GET params:** `?status=new&page=1&limit=20`

---

### Dealers — `/api/v1/dealers`
| Method | URL | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dealers` | List active dealers *(public)* |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dealers/apply` | Submit dealer application *(public)* |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dealers/applications` | List all applications *(admin)* |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/dealers/applications/:id/status` | Approve / reject *(admin)* |

**Auto-promotion:** Approving an application automatically creates a [Dealer](file:///c:/Users/prana/Desktop/krushikendra/controllers/dealerController.js#22-51) document.

**GET params:** `?district=pune`  
**PUT body:** `{ "status": "approved" | "rejected", "reviewedBy": "Admin", "adminNote": "..." }`

